<h2>Index</h2>

<strong>Welcome to Torn Tracks</strong>
<p>This index gives an overview of all the ways of searching the Torn Tracks collection
  that are currently available, and gives an insight into the ones that are planned for the future.
</p><br>

<p><strong>Field Guide</strong>: The tracks are sorted on name, meaning that all
  versions of one track are collected together.
</p>

<p><strong>Chronology</strong>: The tracks are sorted chronologically, on the date
  they were finished.
</p>

<p><strong>Locations</strong>: The tracks are sorted on location, which is the place
  where they were finished.
</p>

<p><strong>Pitch</strong>: The tracks are sorted on pitch, which is the calculated
  average pitch of each track.
</p>
